<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>OpenShift Scaling Demo</title>
        <style>
            html { background: #000; }
            body {
                height: 100vh;
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;

                font-family: sans-serif;
                background-color: {{ color }}E0;

                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: stretch;
            }
            .content {
                text-align: center;
                background-color: {{ color }};
                width: 800px;
                border-left: 4px solid #00000080;
                border-right: 4px solid #00000080;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Scaling with OpenShift &#128640;</h1>
            <p>Different replicas will (<em>possibly</em>) show different colors.</p>
            <p><strong>&quot;Source&quot;</strong> is the default routing strategy, so the user will be routed to the same instance,</p>
            <p>And therefore see the same color even after reload.</p>
        <div>
    </body>
</html>
